class KadasMilxAnnotationController : KadasAnnotationItemController
{
%Docstring(signature="appended")
Controller for \c KadasMilxAnnotationItem (type id \c "kadas:milx").

Stub implementation. The legacy \c KadasMilxItem driving libmss IPC (\c
KadasMilxClient) is being ported in slices 35+; for now this controller
only provides identity and a factory so the type registers cleanly with
\c KadasAnnotationControllerRegistry. All draw/edit hooks are no-ops
that return sensible empty defaults — drawing new MILX symbols is not
yet supported through the annotation map tools.
%End

